Executive Profile
Thomas W. Storey  Independent Director, Summit Hotel Properties, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 4 different industries.See Board Relationships60$186,570
Background

		Mr. Thomas W. Storey, also known as Tom, has been an Independent Director of Summit Hotel Properties, Inc. since February 9, 2011. Mr. Storey has been a Trustee of Legacy Hotels Real Estate Investment Trust since December 12, 2006. He serves as a Director of Summit Hotel Gp Llc-General Partner at Summit Hotel OP, LP. Mr. Storey served as the President of Hospitality at LodgeNet Interactive Corporation since April 2013. He served as Executive Vice President of Development ... at Fairmont Hotels & Resorts Inc. since July 2004. Mr. Storey served as an Executive Vice President of Business Development and Strategy at Fairmont Hotels & Resorts Inc. from October 1, 2001 to July 2004. Since February 1996, he served as President of Club Hotels by Doubletree. From August 1986 to August 1989, Mr. Storey served in a variety of senior management positions with Marriott Hotels Corporation. He served as an Executive Vice President of Corporate Strategic Planning and Venture Operations at Promus Hotel Corporation since February 1999. From August 1989 to July 1994, he served as an Executive Vice President of Sales and Marketing at Radisson Hotels International. Mr. Storey was with Promus Hotels, as Executive Vice President Strategic Planning and Venture Operations from 1998 until 2000 and Executive Vice President Marketing from 1997 to 1998. Prior to joining Promus Hotels, from August 1994 to 1997, he was an Executive Vice President of Sales and Marketing at Doubletree Hotels Corporation. He was employed at Candlewood Hotel Company, Inc. He served as the Chairman of the Board of Summit Hotel Properties, Inc. from July 30, 2015 to January 18, 2017. Mr. Storey holds a Master's of Business Administration Degree from Cornell University and a Bachelor's Degree in Economics from Bates College.Read Full Background




